  "ID": "200801-13",
  "Title": "ngIRCd: Denial of service",
  "Synopsis": "\n    ngIRCd does not properly sanitize commands sent by users, allowing for a\n    Denial of Service.\n  ",
  "Product": {
    "Text": "ngircd",
    "Type": "ebuild"
